{"tid":327574,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"難聽啲講句 丈部分肥婆真係好撚八婆","createTime":"2017-07-19T01:01:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T04:59:21.000Z","uid":73238,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e8a520cfa23e1e4683bc9c5db4b97f430468b9b4","tid":327574,"uid":73238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:01:10.000Z","msg":"我講嘅肥婆唔係指有個肚腩仔喎<br />\n係離遠睇都覺得大份喎<br />\n<br />\n先講下我一直以黎預到嘅肥婆<br />\n<br />\n1. 啲仔明明同緊其他女吹水 肥婆都可以走黎搭嗲串下你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   其實係咪冇仔同你吹水想過黎r？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實你好聲氣點會冇人同你傾計<br />\n<br />\n2. 呢類自信肥婆 你自己肥都好啦 走去人身攻擊人 博乜？ 博比人攻擊返囉 之後又唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 仆你個街 自己冇仔陪 痴埋啲女度 都冇問題<br />\n屌你痴埋啲正正常常嘅女 其他仔想行埋去條女度都好似要過左你關先。。好似自己冇人要就要其他姊妹陪你冇人要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後我想講肥婆唔係個個都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但大部分都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e41f80e2331a595284dad0925be0ec4e69256a","tid":327574,"uid":73238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:02:56.000Z","msg":"標題自膠打錯字<br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大部分</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8fdf24a5590bf2e7b371a85a81d1bee0aa503ab","tid":327574,"uid":73238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a2aead92b44f724f84c8e0df2f9f7e3f3004d82","tid":327574,"uid":73238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:14:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hk